GET http://localhost:8000/

###

### Get All Patients
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patients

###

### Get All Prompts
GET http://localhost:8000/api/prompts

###

### Get Demo Scenarios
GET http://localhost:8000/api/scenarios

###

### Submit Scenario A (Should Approve)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/submit-request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "P001",
  "drug_requested": "Ozempic",
  "diagnosis_code": "E11.9",
  "requesting_doctor": "Dr. Mehta"
}

###

