###

### Update a Prompt (Prompt Studio test)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/prompts/critic_agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agent": "critic_agent",
  "system_prompt": "You are a VERY strict adversarial critic. Find every possible flaw. Be aggressive in your review. Return only valid JSON as specified."
}
